snippet: LEAD: After a controversy over whether they should be allowed to compete in the 1990 Jumping Frog Jubilee, three African Goliath frogs fizzled in the competition on Sunday, allowing a California frog to win....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: After a controversy over whether they should be allowed to compete in the 1990 Jumping Frog Jubilee, three African Goliath frogs fizzled in the competition on Sunday, allowing a California frog to win.

headline.main: A Little Frog Outleaps Some Large Outsiders
